comments.body: There are some physical differences, but they're often not as pronounced as the examples you will find online and are most pronounced in bulls. Location is the main giveaway, as the Yellowstone herds are probably the truest/purest Plains bison ssp.
Is it location that would tell me that? Or something visible? Thanks in advance for letting me know.

results.place_guess: Yellowstone National Park, Teton County, US-WY, US
